body:
### About 4 Queens Project.
Created for a Math 370 (Graph Theory) project. This helps the students understand how graph theory can be applied to a real world problem. The queen objects were created using Blender.

### Authors and Contributors
In 2016, Scott Lowry (@slowry1) created the 4 Queens Unity project.
